First combine over the common denominator \(y+8\):  
\[
\frac{y^2}{y+8}-\frac{64}{y+8}
=\frac{y^2-64}{y+8}
=\frac{(y-8)(y+8)}{y+8}
=y-8,
\]  
provided \(y+8\neq0\).  

